    "title": "Sobre o Editor - Leivis Lima",
    "description": "Conheça Leivis Lima, idealizador do AuditEduca. Contador, Auditor Independente e facilitador de conhecimento com experiência Big4.",
    "html": "<section class='py-20 lg:py-32 relative overflow-hidden'>\n    <!-- Background Pattern -->\n    <div class='absolute inset-0 opacity-5 dark:opacity-10'>\n        <div class='absolute inset-0' style='background-image: radial-gradient(circle at 1px 1px, rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.4) 1px, transparent 0); background-size: 40px 40px;'></div>\n    </div>\n    \n    <div class='max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative'>\n        <!-- Breadcrumb -->\n        <nav class='flex items-center space-x-2 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-8'>\n            <a href='#' class='hover:text-audit-blue dark:hover:text-audit-gold transition-colors'>\n                <i class='fas fa-home mr-1'></i> Início\n            </a>\n            <i class='fas fa-chevron-right text-xs'></i>\n            <a href='institucional.html' class='hover:text-audit-blue dark:hover:text-audit-gold transition-colors'>\n                Institucional\n            </a>\n            <i class='fas fa-chevron-right text-xs'></i>\n            <span class='text-audit-blue dark:text-audit-gold font-medium'>Sobre o Editor</span>\n        </nav>\n        \n        <div class='text-center mb-16'>\n            <span class='inline-block py-2 px-6 rounded-full bg-blue-500/10 dark:bg-blue-400/20 text-blue-700 dark:text-blue-400 text-sm font-bold tracking-wider mb-6 border border-blue-500/20 dark:border-blue-400/30'>\n                SOBRE O EDITOR\n            </span>\n            <h1 class='text-4xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-audit-navy dark:text-white mb-6 leading-tight'>\n                Leivis Lima\n            </h1>\n            <p class='text-xl lg:text-2xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto'>\n                Contador, Auditor Independente e Facilitador de Conhecimento\n            </p>\n        </div>\n        \n        <!-- Profile Section -->\n        <div class='grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-20 items-center mb-20'>\n            <!-- Photo -->\n            <div class='text-center lg:text-left'>\n                <div class='relative inline-block'>\n                    <div class='w-80 h-80 rounded-full overflow-hidden mx-auto lg:mx-0 border-8 border-audit-gold dark:border-audit-goldDark shadow-2xl transform hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300'>\n                        <img src='https://auditeduca.com.br/assets/images/about-creator.webp' alt='Leivis Lima - Idealizador do AuditEduca' class='w-full h-full object-cover'>\n                    </div>\n                    <!-- Floating elements -->\n                    <div class='absolute -top-4 -right-4 w-12 h-12 bg-audit-gold rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg animate-pulse-gold'>\n                        <i class='fas fa-award text-white text-lg'></i>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class='absolute -bottom-4 -left-4 w-12 h-12 bg-audit-blue rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg'>\n                        <i class='fas fa-graduation-cap text-white text-lg'></i>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <!-- Bio -->\n            <div class='space-y-6'>\n                <div class='space-y-4'>\n                    <h2 class='text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-audit-navy dark:text-white'>\n                        Seja bem-vindo(a) ao Audit Educa\n                    </h2>\n                    <p class='text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed'>\n                        Me chamo Leivis, sou Contador e Auditor Independente, mas gosto de me definir essencialmente como um <strong class='text-audit-gold dark:text-audit-goldDark'>facilitador de conhecimento</strong>.\n                    </p>\n                </div>\n                \n                <div class='bg-white/80 dark:bg-gray-800/80 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-6 border border-gray-200/50 dark:border-gray-700/50 shadow-lg'>\n                    <div class='flex items-start space-x-3'>\n                        <div class='flex-shrink-0'>\n                            <div class='w-10 h-10 bg-audit-gold/10 dark:bg-audit-goldDark/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center'>\n                                <i class='fas fa-briefcase text-audit-gold dark:text-audit-goldDark text-lg'></i>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                        <div>\n                            <h3 class='font-bold text-audit-navy dark:text-white mb-2'>Experiência Big4</h3>\n                            <p class='text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm'>\n                                Carreira forjada no rigor das maiores empresas de auditoria do mundo (Big4), onde cheguei ao cargo de Gerente\n                            </p>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        \n        <!-- Main Story -->\n        <div class='max-w-4xl mx-auto'>\n            <div class='bg-white/90 dark:bg-gray-800/90 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-8 lg:p-12 shadow-xl border border-gray-200/50 dark:border-gray-700/50'>\n                <div class='prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert max-w-none'>\n                    <div class='space-y-6 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed'>\n                        <p class='text-lg'>\n                            Nestas empresas, tive a oportunidade de aprender profundamente sobre <strong class='text-audit-blue'>modelos de negócios</strong> e como aplicar a <strong class='text-audit-gold'>contabilidade e a auditoria</strong> no contexto prático das empresas que conheci.\n                        </p>\n                        \n                        <p>\n                            No entanto, percebi que a aplicabilidade prática muitas vezes era ensinada de forma desnecessariamente complexa. Devido ao volume de trabalho e aos prazos apertados do mundo corporativo, o treinamento acabava sendo <span class='font-semibold text-red-600 dark:text-red-400'>deficitário ou até mesmo negligenciado</span>.\n                        </p>\n                        \n                        <div class='bg-gradient-to-r from-audit-blue/10 to-audit-gold/10 dark:from-audit-blue/20 dark:to-audit-gold/20 rounded-xl p-6 border-l-4 border-audit-gold'>\n                            <p class='text-lg font-medium text-audit-navy dark:text-white mb-2'>\n                                <i class='fas fa-heart text-audit-gold mr-2'></i>Missão Pessoal\n                            </p>\n                            <p>\n                                Sabendo dessa deficiência, sempre procurei desenvolver os profissionais que tive a oportunidade de liderar ao longo da minha carreira. Considero que <strong class='text-audit-gold'>desenvolver pessoas — tanto técnica quanto comportamentalmente</strong> — é uma missão e o maior legado que podemos deixar para as novas gerações da área contábil.\n                            </p>\n                        </div>\n                        \n                        <div class='bg-gradient-to-r from-green-50 to-blue-50 dark:from-green-900/20 dark:to-blue-900/20 rounded-xl p-6 border border-green-200 dark:border-green-700'>\n                            <h3 class='text-xl font-bold text-audit-navy dark:text-white mb-3'>\n                                <i class='fas fa-lightbulb text-audit-gold mr-2'></i>O Audit Educa Nasce\n                            </h3>\n                            <p>\n                                O Audit Educa <strong class='text-green-600 dark:text-green-400'>nasce dessa paixão por ensinar</strong>. Aqui, combino a experiência técnica e comportamental adquirida ao longo dos anos com minha nova paixão: o <strong class='text-audit-blue'>desenvolvimento web</strong> e o <strong class='text-purple-600'>\"vibecoding\"</strong>.\n                            </p>\n                        </div>\n                        \n                        <p>\n                            Eu mesmo projeto e codifico os conteúdos e as ferramentas que você vê aqui. Procuro <strong class='text-audit-gold'>simplificar o complexo</strong>, criando um site que sirva de apoio real ao seu desenvolvimento educacional e profissional.\n                        </p>\n                        \n                        <div class='text-center bg-gradient-to-r from-audit-navy to-audit-blue rounded-xl p-8 text-white'>\n                            <p class='text-lg font-medium mb-2'>\n                                <i class='fas fa-users mr-2'></i>Para Quem é este Espaço\n                            </p>\n                            <p class='text-xl'>\n                                Seja você um <strong>estudante</strong> ou um <strong>profissional contábil experiente</strong>, este espaço é para você.\n                            </p>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>\n\n<!-- Credentials Section -->\n<section class='py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-audit-navy via-audit-blue to-audit-navy dark:from-gray-900 dark:via-gray-800 dark:to-gray-900'>\n    <div class='max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8'>\n        <div class='text-center mb-16'>\n            <h2 class='text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6'>\n                Credenciais Profissionais\n            </h2>\n            <p class='text-xl text-gray-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto'>\n                Registros oficiais que comprovam minha qualificação profissional\n            </p>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class='grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto'>\n            <!-- CRC Credential -->\n            <div class='text-center group'>\n                <div class='relative inline-block mb-6'>\n                    <div class='w-48 h-48 mx-auto rounded-full overflow-hidden bg-white p-6 shadow-2xl transform group-hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300'>\n                        <img src='assets/imgs/1000305434.png' alt='Contador Habilitado - CRC' class='w-full h-full object-contain'>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class='absolute -top-2 -right-2 w-8 h-8 bg-audit-gold rounded-full flex items-center justify-center animate-pulse'>\n                        <i class='fas fa-certificate text-white text-sm'></i>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class='text-white'>\n                    <h3 class='text-2xl font-bold mb-2'>Contador Habilitado</h3>\n                    <p class='text-gray-300'>Registro junto ao CRC</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <!-- CNAI Credential -->\n            <div class='text-center group'>\n                <div class='relative inline-block mb-6'>\n                    <div class='w-48 h-48 mx-auto rounded-full overflow-hidden bg-white p-6 shadow-2xl transform group-hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300'>\n                        <img src='assets/imgs/1000305435.png' alt='Auditor Independente - CNAI' class='w-full h-full object-contain'>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class='absolute -top-2 -right-2 w-8 h-8 bg-green-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center animate-pulse'>\n                        <i class='fas fa-shield-alt text-white text-sm'></i>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class='text-white'>\n                    <h3 class='text-2xl font-bold mb-2'>Auditor Independente</h3>\n                    <p class='text-gray-300'>Registro CNAI</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>\n\n<!-- Closing Section -->\n<section class='py-20 relative'>\n    <div class='max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center'>\n        <div class='bg-gradient-to-r from-audit-gold/10 to-audit-blue/10 dark:from-audit-gold/20 dark:to-audit-blue/20 rounded-2xl p-8 lg:p-12 border border-audit-gold/20'>\n            <div class='max-w-3xl mx-auto'>\n                <h2 class='text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-audit-navy dark:text-white mb-6'>\n                    Atenciosamente,\n                </h2>\n                <p class='text-xl text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8'>\n                    <strong>Leivis Lima</strong><br>\n                    <span class='text-audit-gold dark:text-audit-goldDark font-semibold'>\n                        Idealizador do Audit Educa\n                    </span>\n                </p>\n                \n                <!-- Logo Section -->\n                <div class='flex flex-col items-center space-y-6'>\n                    <div class='w-32 h-32 mx-auto rounded-xl overflow-hidden bg-white shadow-lg p-4'>\n                        <img src='assets/imgs/1000305429.png' alt='Logotipo Audit Educa' class='w-full h-full object-contain'>\n                    </div>\n                    <p class='text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 italic'>\n                        Logotipo Audit Educa\n                    </p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>"
}
